Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:05.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禮物的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.00,0:00:10.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其一  通常
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.68,0:00:14.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小佐和在修學旅行的時候買了什麼禮物？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.00,0:00:16.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是這個哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.76,0:00:17.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木刀？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.86,0:00:20.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說到禮物的話通常就是這個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.98,0:00:22.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.06,0:00:25.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說到通常的話當然就是這個了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.88,0:00:27.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,京都也有啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.56,0:00:28.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.48,0:00:31.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,努力咯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.48,0:00:31.07,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（どすえ:京都語，同です）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.31,0:00:33.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都是通常的禮物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.72,0:00:36.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  難得去一次京都
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.74,0:00:40.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就得買京都特色的東西嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.44,0:00:42.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真買了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.03,0:00:51.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禮物的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.03,0:00:56.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其二  各式各樣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.33,0:01:00.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是旅行的禮物也不盡是物品吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.08,0:01:04.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如照片  或者印象深刻的回憶之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.92,0:01:07.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  照片的話拍了很多哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.81,0:01:08.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.55,0:01:10.52,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（包子鋪）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.52,0:01:11.52,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（京都年糕）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.52,0:01:12.52,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（京都果凍）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.52,0:01:13.52,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（塔式巧克力）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.11,0:01:13.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.94,0:01:18.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禮物…而且全是吃的照片啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.66,0:01:24.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒法全買下…就只能拍下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.67,0:01:31.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澪學姐真的買了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.73,0:01:34.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  看起來很好吃…順手就買了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.07,0:01:37.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  小澪好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.45,0:01:40.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  但是保質期都是今天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.96,0:01:41.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好啦  澪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.94,0:01:47.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超過保質期的話  裡面就會變得濕嗒嗒黏糊糊哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.46,0:01:48.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.49,0:01:50.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要在今天全部吃完才行
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.10,0:02:02.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禮物的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.10,0:02:07.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其三  標題
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.57,0:02:10.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,律學姐買了什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.20,0:02:11.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.71,0:02:13.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,64色圓珠筆
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.32,0:02:15.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.09,0:02:18.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然看起來有點難用  但好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.19,0:02:20.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  小澪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.60,0:02:24.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用這個來寫「毛筆與圓珠筆」Ver.2的歌詞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.68,0:02:28.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,標題就用「毛筆與64色圓珠筆」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.87,0:02:32.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…寫不出來吧！
